<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629082>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–17. Microdacne gloriousa sp. nov.: 9–11) habitus, holotype; 9) dorsal view; 10) ventral view; 11) lateral view; 12) ovipositor, allotype; 13) spermatheca, allotype; 14–17) Male genitalia, paratype; 14) abdominal segment VIII–IX, ventral view; 15) tegmen, dorsal view; 16) penis, lateral view; 17) penis, dorsal view. Scale bars: 9–11 = 1.0 mm; 12, 14–17 = 0.2 mm; 13 = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4629082/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629084>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18–22. Microdacne lamingtonia sp. nov., holotype: 18–19) habitus; 18) dorsal view; 19) ventral view; 20) lateral view; 21) spermatheca; 22) ovipositor. Scale bars: 18–19 = 1.0 mm, 21 = 0.1 mm, 22 = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4629084/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629080>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–8. Echinothallis banderbearella sp. nov.: 1–3) habitus, holotype; 1) dorsal view; 2) ventral view; 3) lateral view; 4) female genitalia, allotype; 5–8) male genitalia, paratype; 5) abdominal segments VIII–IX, ventral view; 6) tegmen, dorsal view; 7) penis, lateral view; 8) penis, dorsal view. Scale bars: 1–3 = 1.0 mm, 4–8 = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4629080/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4629090>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33–40. Episcaphula (Tropidoscaphula) megalodacnoides sp. nov.: 33–36) holotype; 33) dorsal view; 34) ventral view; 35) lateral view; 36) head, front view; 37) female genitalia, allotype; 38–40) male genitalia, paratype; 38) abdominal segment VIII–IX, ventral view; 39) tegmen, dorsal view; 40) penis, lateral view. Scale bars: 34–35 = 2.0 mm, 36 = 1.0 mm, 37–40 = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4629090/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

